'''[[File:Wall_tower_barrikade.png|right]]Barricades''' neutralize the troop strength of a limited number of enemy cavalry units. Neutralized attackers will not deal damage to defenders. A maximum of 50% of cavalry attackers will be affected. Barricades can only be built on the outer ring of the City Wall, and don’t count towards a city’s building number limit.

